{"tid":675914,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"三星宣布5nm、4nm、3nm製程！採用全新電晶體管架構","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-26T10:03:50.000Z","uid":141060,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"5849ea9784b87545f0ab28a5b6a9472b359fcb19","tid":675914,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:52:52.000Z","msg":"這兩年，三星電子、台積電在半導體製程上一路狂奔，雖然有技術之爭但把曾經的領導者Intel遠遠甩在身後已經是不爭的事實。<br />\n<br />\n在美國舉行的三星製程論壇SFF 2018 USA之上，三星更是宣布將連續進軍5nm、4nm、3nm工藝製程，直逼物理極限！<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201805/24/004548pcddxkjdx588thk8.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201805%2F24%2F004548pcddxkjdx588thk8.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=9bc5a6b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在美國舉行的三星製程論壇SFF 2018 USA之上，三星更是宣布將連續進軍5nm、4nm、3nm製程，直逼物理極限！三星宣布5nm、4nm、3nm工藝！ 高性能低功耗兼顧<br />\n<br />\n7LPP (7nm Low Power Plus)<br />\n<br />\n三星將在7LPP製程上首次應用EUV極紫外光刻技術，預計今年下半年投產。關鍵IP正在研發中，明年上半年完成。<br />\n<br />\n5LPE (5nm Low Power Early)<br />\n<br />\n在7LPP製程的基礎上繼續創新改進，可進一步縮小晶片核心面積，帶來超低功耗。<br />\n<br />\n4LPE/LPP (4nm Low Power Early/Plus)<br />\n<br />\n最後一次應用高度成熟和行業驗證的FinFET立體電晶體管技術，結合此前5LPE製程的成熟技術，晶片面積更小，性能更高，可以快速達到高良率量產，也方便客戶升級。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.xfastest.com/data/attachment/forum/201805/24/004728l99dsem98gdld7i8.jpg.thumb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.xfastest.com%2Fdata%2Fattachment%2Fforum%2F201805%2F24%2F004728l99dsem98gdld7i8.jpg.thumb.jpg&h=6985f3b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGate-All-Around就是環繞柵極，相比於現在的FinFET Tri-Gate三柵極設計，將重新設計電晶體管底層結構，克服當前技術的物理、性能極限，增強柵極控制，性能大大提升。三星的GAA技術叫做MBCFET (Multi-Bridge-Channel FET)。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能以為三星的製程主要用來生產行動處理器等低功耗設備，但其實在高性能領域，三星也準備了殺手鐧，大規模數據中心、AI人工智慧、ML機器學習，7LPP和後續製程都能提供服務，並有一整套平台解決方案。<br />\n<br />\n譬如高速的100Gbps+ SerDes(串行轉換解串器)，三星就設計了2.5D/3D異構封裝技術。而針對5G、車聯網領域的低功耗微控制器(MCU)、下代聯網設備，三星也將提供全套完整的平台方案，從28/18nm eMRA/RF到10/8nm FinFET任君選擇。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d42ac8624429d6fabd34f4f9b870130704d598ce","tid":675914,"uid":36651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c944aa8b97df0c99ecc3f2108a17dd43264eb191","tid":675914,"uid":77104,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:47:49.000Z","msg":"中國追唔到拉"},{"pid":"d795a1111a3fa608eed862016b0e5afa73b18924","tid":675914,"uid":39365,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:54:50.000Z","msg":"外國盲目追求縮細晶片增加效能, 浪費資源, 中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc0baba8e446b61fc114d09a7063ddf7d7e32ca7","tid":675914,"uid":59511,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:00:27.000Z","msg":"中國下年先買到7nm光刻機，或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e130357df2f919629e0749312e5460ab11dcd97c","tid":675914,"uid":5159,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:02:58.000Z","msg":"到時中國一早發明左時光機啦"},{"pid":"31309776643b89f93719fcd9a425639702c18686","tid":675914,"uid":1518,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"順帶一提GAA係samsung,IBM,GF共同研究，三星用GAA,似乎GF好大機會都會用"},{"pid":"5de80b5c19566b5dc595355865911271040a9d7e","tid":675914,"uid":37820,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:22:27.000Z","msg":"三叔又唔知收買咗幾多台積電內鬼"},{"pid":"9686d7a41fa68275c94ae7f0fef5f2245c36cea8","tid":675914,"uid":68094,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:23:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"363dbc4af36cbe18c6a525c4a57d7bf0fcdf020c","tid":675914,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"基本上3nm應用係電話上面<br />\n至少都有5日續航力"},{